! ospfd configuration for node {{NODE_ID}}
hostname {{NODE_ID}}
!
! Every link is a /30 between exactly two routers, so each interface is treated as
! point-to-point: this skips broadcast DR election (and its wait timer), letting
! adjacencies reach Full and reconverge within the test's convergence budget. Fast
! hello/dead timers keep failure detection well under convergence_timeout_ms.
{{OSPF_INTERFACES}}
router ospf
 ospf router-id {{ROUTER_ID}}
 redistribute connected
 timers throttle spf 0 50 5000
{{OSPF_NETWORKS}}
!
line vty
!
